  "title": "QUANTITY SURVEYOR",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Quantity Surveyor for Interior Design Firm</strong></u></p>\n<p>-Attend tender interviews &amp; site show</p>\n<p>-Preparation and analyse costing for tenders</p>\n<p>-Preparation and submission progress claims, VO and finalization of project accounts.</p>\n<p>-To source quotations for relevant trade works including price comparison and cost analysis</p>\n<p>-Ensure the construction project is completed within its projected budget</p>\n<p>-Verify claims for variation and payments</p>\n<p>-Analyse outcomes and write detailed progress reports</p>\n<p>-Other ad-hoc duties from the Management</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirement</p>\n<p>-Diploma/Degree in Quantity Surveying</p>\n<p>-Able to work independently</p>\n<p>-Must proficient in use Microsoft Office &amp; AutoCad</p>\n<p>-Knowledge of contract administration &amp; tender procedures is an advantage</p>\n<p>-Min 3 years relevant experience</p>",
